###Opt-in company newsletter 

> Request:

```shell
curl -X POST \
  <%= config[:api_host] %>/v1/partner/referrals/company-newsletters \
  -H 'authorization: Bearer your-account-token' \
  -H 'content-type: application/json' \
  -H 'cache-control: no-cache' \
  -d '
  {
    "name": "John Doe",
    "email": "john.doe@nospam.com"
  }'
```

```csharp
var client = new RestClient("<%= config[:api_host] %>/v1");
var request = new RestRequest("partner/referrals/company-newsletters", Method.POST);
request.AddHeader("authorization", "Bearer {token}");
request.AddHeader("content-type", "application/json");
request.AddHeader("cache-control", "no-cache");
request.AddJsonBody(new
{
  name = "John Doe",
  email = "john.doe@nospam.com"
});
var response = client.Execute(request);
```

> Response:

```
201 Created
```

<api>`POST /v1/partner/referrals/company-newsletters`</api>

Signs a contact up for MicroTek's news company letter

Parameter | Type | Description
--------- | ---- | -----------
name **required** | *string* | Persons full name
email **required** | *string* | Persons email address
